默认情况下，UrlBasedViewResolver 可以把没有绑定的view以模板形式解析
但是，我们希望使用相同的扩展名，比如 *.html，而不是一个*.html,一个 *.htm

As an example, with JSP as a view technology, 
you can use the UrlBasedViewResolver. 
This view resolver translates a view name to a URL and hands the request over to the 
RequestDispatcher to render the view.

